---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 504
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Trust in God
  - 296
By: Ibn al-'Arif
---
Among the gifts that God grants to His slave, when he obeys Him and
submits to His service and follows this way all his life ... (is) that
He will guarantee for him the means of livelihood, sending him along
from state to state, without effort or anxiety.
